00104 //! Calcule la conductivite
00105 void Loi_Etat_Multi_GP_base::calculer_lambda()
00106 {
00107   const Champ_Don& mu = le_fluide->viscosite_dynamique();
00108   const DoubleTab& tab_mu = mu.valeurs();
00109   Champ_Don& lambda = le_fluide->conductivite();
00110   DoubleTab& tab_lambda = lambda.valeurs();
00111   const DoubleTab& tab_Cp = le_fluide->capacite_calorifique().valeurs();
00112   int i, n = tab_lambda.size();
00113 
00114 // La conductivite est soit un champ uniforme soit calculee a partir de la viscosite dynamique et du Pr
00115   if (sub_type(Champ_Fonc_Tabule,lambda.valeur()))
00116     {
00117       lambda.valeur().mettre_a_jour(temperature_.valeur().temps());
00118       return;
00119     }
00120   if (!sub_type(Champ_Uniforme,lambda.valeur()))
00121     {
00122       if (sub_type(Champ_Uniforme,mu.valeur()))
00123         {
00124           double mu0 = tab_mu(0,0);
00125           for (i=0 ; i<n ; i++)  tab_lambda(i,0) = mu0 * Cp_ / Pr_;
00126         }
00127       else
00128         for (i=0 ; i<n ; i++) tab_lambda(i,0) = tab_mu(i,0) * tab_Cp(i,0) / Pr_;
00129     }
00130   tab_lambda.echange_espace_virtuel();
00131   Debog::verifier("tab_lambda",tab_lambda);
00132 }

00147 //! Calcule la diffusivite
00148 void Loi_Etat_Multi_GP_base::calculer_alpha()
00149 {
00150   const Champ_Don& lambda = le_fluide->conductivite();
00151   const DoubleTab& tab_lambda = lambda.valeurs();
00152   Champ_Don& alpha=le_fluide->diffusivite();
00153   DoubleTab& tab_alpha = le_fluide->diffusivite().valeurs();
00154   const DoubleTab& tab_rho = le_fluide->masse_volumique().valeurs();
00155   const DoubleTab& tab_Cp = le_fluide->capacite_calorifique().valeurs();
00156   int i, n = tab_alpha.size(), isVDF = 0;
00157   if (alpha.valeur().que_suis_je()=="Champ_Fonc_P0_VDF") isVDF = 1;
00158 
00159   if (isVDF)
00160     {
00161       if (sub_type(Champ_Uniforme,lambda.valeur()))
00162         {
00163           double lambda0 = tab_lambda(0,0);
00164           for (i=0 ; i<n ; i++)  tab_alpha(i,0) = lambda0 / ( tab_rho(i,0) * tab_Cp(i,0) );
00165         }
00166       else
00167         {
00168           for (i=0 ; i<n ; i++) tab_alpha(i,0) = tab_lambda(i,0) / ( tab_rho(i,0) * tab_Cp(i,0) );
00169         }
00170     }
00171   else //!< VEF
00172     {
00173       const IntTab& elem_faces=ref_cast(Zone_VF,le_fluide->vitesse().zone_dis_base()).elem_faces();
00174       double rhoelem, Cpelem;
00175       int face, nfe = elem_faces.line_size();
00176 
00177       if (sub_type(Champ_Uniforme,lambda.valeur()))
00178         {
00179           double lambda0 = tab_lambda(0,0);
00180           for (i=0 ; i<n ; i++)
00181             {
00182               rhoelem = 0;
00183               Cpelem = 0;
00184               for (face=0; face<nfe; face++)
00185                 {
00186                   rhoelem += tab_rho(elem_faces(i,face),0);
00187                   Cpelem += tab_Cp(elem_faces(i,face),0);
00188                 }
00189               rhoelem /= nfe;
00190               Cpelem /= nfe;
00191               tab_alpha(i,0) = lambda0 / ( rhoelem * Cpelem );
00192             }
00193         }
00194       else
00195         {
00196           for (i=0 ; i<n ; i++)
00197             {
00198               rhoelem = 0;
00199               Cpelem = 0;
00200               for (face=0; face<nfe; face++)
00201                 {
00202                   rhoelem += tab_rho(elem_faces(i,face),0);
00203                   Cpelem += tab_Cp(elem_faces(i,face),0);
00204                 }
00205               rhoelem /= nfe;
00206               Cpelem /= nfe;
00207               tab_alpha(i,0) = tab_lambda(i,0) / ( rhoelem * Cpelem );
00208             }
00209         }
00210     }
00211   tab_alpha.echange_espace_virtuel();
00212   Debog::verifier("alpha",tab_alpha);
00213 }

00257 void Loi_Etat_Multi_GP_base::calculer_tab_mu(const DoubleTab& mu, int size)
00258 {
00259 // Dynamic viscosity is on elem
00260   DoubleTab& tab_mu = le_fluide->viscosite_dynamique().valeurs();
00261   const int nb_elem = tab_mu.size();
00262   if (nb_elem==size) //!< VDF
00263     {
00264       for (int elem=0; elem < nb_elem; elem++) tab_mu(elem,0) = mu(elem);
00265     }
00266   else //!< VEF (average on elem from values on face);
00267     {
00268       const IntTab& elem_faces=ref_cast(Zone_VF,le_fluide->vitesse().zone_dis_base()).elem_faces();
00269       const int nfe = elem_faces.line_size();
00270       tab_mu = 0;
00271       for (int elem=0; elem<nb_elem; elem++)
00272         {
00273           for (int face = 0; face < nfe; face++) tab_mu(elem,0) += mu(elem_faces(elem, face));
00274 
00275           tab_mu(elem,0) /= nfe;
00276         }
00277     }
00278   tab_mu.echange_espace_virtuel();
00279   Debog::verifier("tab_mu", tab_mu);
00280 }
